        <num>CC 1551</num>
        <heading>1551.  Effects of acceptance</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1551.  Effects of acceptance
A donation is effective upon acceptance.  When the donation is effective, the ownership or other real right in the thing given is transferred to the donee.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=108875</p>
